Test client git repo with lazy blob/tree objects.

  $ . $TESTDIR/git.sh
  $ git -c init.defaultBranch=main init -q server-repo
  $ cd server-repo
  $ SL_IDENTITY=sl drawdag << 'EOS'
  > B  # bookmark main = B
  > |  # B/dir/1=2\n
  > A  # A/dir/1=1\n
  > EOS

Blobs are lazy, trees are not.
